LogicalColumn.name: Total Transaction Amount Last 6 Months
LogicalColumn.Description: This column calculates the total transaction amount of all transactions in the last 6 months, for the customer. The Debit type transaction amount is deducted from the Credit type to calculate this value.

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: SUM("Core"."Fact - CRM - Account Transaction Last 6 Months"."Total Transaction Amount Last 6 Months")

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" = 'Debit' THEN -("%2") WHEN "%1" = 'Credit' THEN "%2" ELSE 0 END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."W_ACCNT_TXN_D"."TXN_TYPE_I" = 'Debit' THEN -("Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."W_ACCNT_TXN_F"."TRANS_AMT") WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."W_ACCNT_TXN_D"."TXN_TYPE_I" = 'Credit' THEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."W_ACCNT_TXN_F"."TRANS_AMT" ELSE 0 END

LogicalColumn.name: % of POS Transactions Last 6 Months
LogicalColumn.Description: This column calculates the % of Transaction in the Last 6 months that were at a Point of Sale. Since a Credit Card may have other transactions like payments, transfers etc. this measure shows the Point of Sale transaction that directly relate to usage.

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" = 0 OR "%1" IS NULL THEN NULL ELSE 100.0d * "%2" / "%1" END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Account Transaction Last 6 Months"."# TXNs Last 6 Months" = 0 OR "Core"."Fact - CRM - Account Transaction Last 6 Months"."# TXNs Last 6 Months" IS NULL THEN NULL ELSE 100.0d * "Core"."Fact - CRM - Account Transaction Last 6 Months"."# of POS TXNs Last 6 Months" / "Core"."Fact - CRM - Account Transaction Last 6 Months"."# TXNs Last 6 Months" END
